{"tid":2512654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一定用緊嘅牌子 原來係呃人嘅！大伏！","createTime":"2021-05-02T02:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T20:10:21.000Z","uid":185909,"like":64,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7ac8f3121ce72b03827806a207afd1809cba8e","tid":2512654,"uid":185909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUZr3KS7fGJYx5eiPKuYKoFYsEFKMEiYNr7PvLePpwcSJ?filename=vx0LsOn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvx0LsOn.png&h=cb361634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麥當勞最近推出左買兩個早餐就可以換一個濕鳩泡泡液，就算換到贈品(左)，長遠都要買梘液(右)!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQKFafYfTcKeHuMTmZhwKm4UMvsPj4bMt8EWbxsLbj6Zh?filename=dfQO911.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfQO911.png&h=15e16cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">▸商家背景◂ 偽德國！威露士來自中國！</span></span><br />\n <br />\n最近疫情之下，賣廣告賣得好勁，標榜來自德國嘅威露士，實情係中國公司，由中國商人左大維於 2000 年喺廣州成立<br />\n <br />\n自稱來自德國，但喺歐洲嘅商標就 2003 年先註冊，仲要有一間叫 Lohmann Haas Pharmaceuticals (CHINA) Limited 嘅公司註冊<br />\n <br />\n為咗扮德國公司扮得更徹底，2019 年 8 月，威露士母公司收購咗一間 1904 年開業叫 Centralin 嘅德國嘅鞋油公司，自此威露士産品就多咗 Centralin 商標及「Germany since 1904」字樣，收購後 Centralin 商標有作出微調，加咗兩粒疑似影射美國莊臣舊商標 &quot;J&quot; 入面嘅圖形<br />\n <br />\n而廣告所指嘅「德國品牌」或 「Germany since 1904」係指收購返來嘅 Centralin 品牌，並非威露士<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"pink\">每次見到巴士大大隻 「快人一泡，德國品牌 」就覺得好賤，明明係大陸野喺度扮德國品牌，其實上面細細隻寫住係佢哋收購centralin 鞋油品牌先係德國品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"0f5c7f48f2742acb4016aff01fb66d6e2b6686e9","tid":2512654,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"一直定一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n照幫推"},{"pid":"1c14373bb0bb904405813bc45101914b9ef80d82","tid":2512654,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那品牌"},{"pid":"0a164a033f26f9da98f5a9a22ea51b1cbbceb580","tid":2512654,"uid":185909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNrgS9T659uVeCZmA1XGZTsnSUQTRC1aymVptXYju6S1Q?filename=voSU5Dj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvoSU5Dj.png&h=1d8e15c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVBmhLFeWQGxPoUhj1dWGDXSK2878SPiFbnoS6tonaffE?filename=KS5GLDk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKS5GLDk.png&h=6b626fd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW3qNnuDJbdHoVvuUqBXbv8rhj4RA1Z6ZpXxrkPz7n2pp?filename=yyPwop1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyyPwop1.png&h=23315418&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmerU3ZoKGbYRxoWGjDxxPVYUYgazb5j8uW3JNj2UHsYoY?filename=YKewop2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKewop2.png&h=8b753253&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW5PwVubkYs9Hy8vhZqR4DoVJhKekLmfHB2KSujkzBdqw?filename=nxO1LDn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxO1LDn.png&h=e6187277&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYzk7J63GTPxkBfAAhQBf2RgGSwbt3EwJJVdghfXsQYbY?filename=vviJewJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvviJewJ.png&h=bad24f93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4997f9d18b3422c66cdcab4acb6205e5e84b18e4","tid":2512654,"uid":185909,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR1o4fA7XwokiEJxshTe99XuqDrayBoQRAW8ikL47t4kw?file